                        <article class="post ">
                            <h3 class="uppercase">PROGRAMA EMERGENCIAL</h3><h4>Ponto a ponto MP 936/2020: Entenda cortes salariais, suspensões e benefício</h4>
                            <ul class="info">
                                <li>
                                    <div class="text date">quinta-feira, 2 de abril de 2020</div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="entyp-pencil-1"></i>
                                    <div class="text">Publicado por CONDUX</div>
                                </li>
                                
                                <li>
                                    <a href="/noticias/?cat=Legisla%E7%E3o+Trabalhista">
                                        <i class="entyp-list-1"></i>
                                        <div class="text">Legislação Trabalhista</div>
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                
                            </ul>
                            
                            <figure>
                                <img src="https://condux.com.br/site/imgnews/272c.jpg" alt="PROGRAMA EMERGENCIAL"/>
                                
                            </figure>
                            
                            <div class="content">
                            
                                <p>
                                    <strong>
                                       A MP 936/2020 possibilita o corte salarial de até 70%, suspensão do contrato de trabalho e benefício emergencial. Entenda ponto a ponto.
                                    </strong>
                                </p>
                            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">O Di&aacute;rio Oficial da Uni&atilde;o publicou nesta quarta-feira, 01, a MP 936/2020 que institui o Programa Emergencial de Manuten&ccedil;&atilde;o do Emprego e da Renda.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Em suma, a norma estabelece o pagamento de um Benef&iacute;cio Emergencial de Preserva&ccedil;&atilde;o do Emprego e da Renda e permite redu&ccedil;&atilde;o de jornadas e sal&aacute;rios e a suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria de contratos de trabalhos.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Essa &eacute; mais uma medida anunciada pelo Governo que tem como objetivo amenizar os Impactos causados com a crise do&nbsp;Coronav&iacute;rus.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Entenda Ponto a Ponto o que muda na MP 936/2020:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Redu&ccedil;&atilde;o de sal&aacute;rios</span></b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Com a MP, o empregador poder&aacute; reduzir os sal&aacute;rios dos funcion&aacute;rios desde que seja de forma proporcional &agrave; jornada de trabalho. Ficam permitidos cortes de 25%, 50% ou 70%, por at&eacute; noventa dias.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">&Eacute; importante ressaltar que o valor do sal&aacute;rio-hora de trabalho do funcion&aacute;rio deve ser mantido.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Suspens&atilde;o do Contrato de Trabalho</span></b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Durante o estado de calamidade p&uacute;blica, o empregador poder&aacute; acordar a suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho de seus empregados, pelo prazo m&aacute;ximo de sessenta dias, que poder&aacute; ser fracionado em at&eacute; dois per&iacute;odos de trinta dias.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">A suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho ser&aacute; pactuada por acordo individual escrito entre empregador e empregado, que ser&aacute; encaminhado ao empregado com anteced&ecirc;ncia de, no m&iacute;nimo, dois dias corridos.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Vale lembrar que a suspens&atilde;o ser&aacute; v&aacute;lida aos empregados com sal&aacute;rio igual ou inferior a R$ 3.135 e aos portadores de diploma de n&iacute;vel superior e que percebam sal&aacute;rio mensal igual ou superior a duas vezes o limite m&aacute;ximo dos benef&iacute;cios do Regime Geral de Previd&ecirc;ncia Social.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">A empresa que tiver auferido, no ano-calend&aacute;rio de 2019, receita bruta superior a R$ 4.800.000,00, somente poder&aacute; suspender o contrato de trabalho de seus empregados mediante o pagamento de ajuda compensat&oacute;ria mensal no valor de trinta por cento do valor do sal&aacute;rio do empregado durante o per&iacute;odo de suspens&atilde;o.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Al&eacute;m disso, se durante o per&iacute;odo de suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho o empregado mantiver as atividades de trabalho, ainda que parcialmente, por meio de teletrabalho, trabalho remoto ou trabalho &agrave; dist&acirc;ncia, ficar&aacute; descaracterizada a suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho e o empregador estar&aacute; sujeito &agrave; penalidades.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt; font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;">Rescis&atilde;o</b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">A dispensa sem justa causa que ocorrer durante o per&iacute;odo de garantia provis&oacute;ria no emprego sujeitar&aacute; o empregador ao pagamento, al&eacute;m das parcelas rescis&oacute;rias previstas na legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o em vigor, de indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o no valor de:</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Redu&ccedil;&atilde;o salarial de 25 &agrave; 50%</span></b><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">: Pagamento de 50% do sal&aacute;rio que o empregado teria direito inicialmente;</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;letter-spacing:.15pt;&#10;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Redu&ccedil;&atilde;o salarial de 50 a 60%</span></b><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">: Pagamento de 75% do sal&aacute;rio que o empregado teria direito inicialmente;</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;letter-spacing:.15pt;&#10;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Redu&ccedil;&atilde;o salarial superior &agrave; 70% ou suspens&atilde;o</span></b><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">: Pagamento de 100% do sal&aacute;rio que o empregado teria direito inicialmente.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Benef&iacute;cio Emergencial</span></b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">O empregador deve informar o Minist&eacute;rio da Economia sobre a redu&ccedil;&atilde;o da jornada de trabalho e de sal&aacute;rio ou a suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho, no prazo de dez dias, contados da data da celebra&ccedil;&atilde;o do acordo.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Dessa forma, o trabalhador poder&aacute; receber um Benef&iacute;cio Emergencial que ser&aacute; pago no prazo de trinta dias da data da celebra&ccedil;&atilde;o do acordo. O valor de tal benef&iacute;cio ter&aacute; como&nbsp;base de c&aacute;lculo&nbsp;o valor mensal do seguro-desemprego a que o empregado teria direito.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">&Eacute; importante ressaltar que o Benef&iacute;cio Emergencial ser&aacute; pago exclusivamente enquanto durar a redu&ccedil;&atilde;o proporcional da jornada de trabalho e de sal&aacute;rio ou a suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Caso o empregador n&atilde;o preste a informa&ccedil;&atilde;o dentro do prazo previsto ficar&aacute; respons&aacute;vel pelo pagamento da remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o no valor anterior &agrave; redu&ccedil;&atilde;o da jornada de trabalho e de sal&aacute;rio ou da suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho do empregado, inclusive dos respectivos encargos sociais, at&eacute; a que informa&ccedil;&atilde;o seja prestada.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">A forma de transmiss&atilde;o dessas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es e comunica&ccedil;&otilde;es, assim como mais detalhes do pagamento do Benef&iacute;cio Emergencial, ser&atilde;o disciplinados pelo Minist&eacute;rio da Economia.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Valor Benef&iacute;cio Emergencial</span></b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">O valor de tal Benef&iacute;cio Emergencial ter&aacute; como&nbsp;base de c&aacute;lculo&nbsp;o valor mensal do seguro-desemprego a que o empregado teria direito, nas seguintes situa&ccedil;&otilde;es:</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">I - na hip&oacute;tese de redu&ccedil;&atilde;o de jornada de trabalho e de sal&aacute;rio, ser&aacute; calculado aplicando-se sobre a&nbsp;base de c&aacute;lculo&nbsp;o percentual da redu&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">II - na hip&oacute;tese de suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria do contrato de trabalho, ter&aacute; valor mensal: equivalente a cem por cento do valor do seguro-desemprego a que o empregado teria direito, ou equivalente a 70% do seguro-desemprego a que o empregado teria direito.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">O empregado com contrato de trabalho intermitente formalizado at&eacute; 1 de abril/2020, far&aacute; jus ao benef&iacute;cio emergencial mensal no valor de R$ 600, pelo per&iacute;odo de tr&ecirc;s meses.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">A norma estabelece que a exist&ecirc;ncia de mais de um contrato de trabalho n&atilde;o gerar&aacute; direito &agrave; concess&atilde;o de mais de um benef&iacute;cio emergencial mensal. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;line-height:normal"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt;">Fonte: Site Cont&aacute;beis</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;&#10;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-fareast-language:PT-BR"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 107%; color: black;"><o:p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></span></o:p></span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&#10;&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
                            </div>
                            
                        </article>
                        
                        
